sentence: What are some of the 400 / 500 level EECS courses with the least workload ?
sentence-with-vars: What are some of the number0/number1 level department0 courses with the least workload ?
sql: SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "EECS" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER < 600 AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER >= 400 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD = 1 ;
sql-with-vars: SELECT DISTINCT COURSEalias0.NAME , COURSEalias0.NUMBER FROM COURSE AS COURSEalias0 INNER JOIN PROGRAM_COURSE AS PROGRAM_COURSEalias0 WHERE COURSEalias0.DEPARTMENT = "department0" AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER < 600 AND COURSEalias0.NUMBER >= number0 AND PROGRAM_COURSEalias0.WORKLOAD = 1 ;
